Posts.Content: JaniceTran wrote: If you are 50 years of age or younger, BRCA positive and have had a prophylactic mastectomy or planning on doing so to decrease your breast cancer risk we need your help! This study will explores the decision making factors of BRCA positive women and their decision to have a prophylactic mastectomy.
